characteristics.name: Response Speed
characteristics.description: This dimension represents the user's typical response time to new information or comments.

characteristics.name: Humor and Tone
characteristics.description: This dimension captures the user's preferred tone in their communication, including any use of humor or sarcasm.

characteristics.name: Emotional Expression
characteristics.description: This dimension represents the user's typical emotional expression in their content, such as enthusiasm or calmness.

characteristics.name: Engagement Level
characteristics.description: This dimension represents the user's typical level of engagement with others' content, such as asking questions or sharing personal thoughts.

characteristics.name: Depth of Thought
characteristics.description: This dimension represents the user's typical level of depth in their thought process, such as providing detailed explanations or keeping topics brief.

characteristics.name: Use of Emotional Language
characteristics.description: This dimension represents the user's typical use of emotional language in their communication, such as metaphors or similes.

characteristics.name: Directness and Honesty
characteristics.description: This dimension represents the user's typical level of directness and honesty in their communication, such as being straightforward or tactful.

characteristics.name: Storytelling Ability
characteristics.description: This dimension represents the user's typical use of storytelling in their communication, such as sharing personal anecdotes or using narratives to illustrate points.
